data.description: This 2019 Stunner has all of the Bells and Whistles!  Gorgeous granite countertops compliment the stainless appliances in the kitchen, Master suite features a walk in closet and a double vanity bathroom with custom tile shower. All living features are on the main floor, PLUS a full finished basement! What you CAN'T see in the photos are all of the personal upgrades: 22 watt Generac generator, Honeywell Smart Thermostats, 500 gallon buried propane tank, and so much more.  A year round stream flows through the bottom portion of the property, making a great opportunity for relaxing space.  Also available (listed separately) is an adjoining lot for added buffer if desired. This Beautiful home is located within one mile of Poteet Creek Recreational area, very close to Public boat access for Lake Nottely.  Quick access to Murphy, NC, Blairsville, and Blue Ridge.  WELCOME HOME!
